Service Replies for Email Usage and Tracking

Service Replies charges only for the activity you use. Learn how your agents interact with Einstein generative AI and track your usage against your subscription allowance.

For each Einstein generative AI feature, agent usage depends on the size of the request and the number of requests. For Service Replies for Email:
The request size depends on the length of the knowledge article.
A request is created each time an agent clicks Draft Einstein Email.
To learn more or get updates on your Service Replies for Email usage, contact your Salesforce Account Executive.
